PrecisEnactment of the ORDER AMENDING THE SCHEDULE TO THE CUSTOMS TARIFF, 1999-3 which extends the June 30, 1999 expiry date of a number of temporary tariff items for an additional three-year period and introduces three new temporary tariff items to extend the duty relieving provisions of the Knitting Yarns Remission Order, 1996, effective July 1, 1999.
